<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TaskManager</title>
   
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/60cc3418d0.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/homepage.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-700 to-blue-600 min-h-screen text-white font-sans flex flex-col items-center">
    <header class="w-full py-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center px-4 md:px-8">
        <a class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-wider text-glow mb-4 md:mb-0" href="#">TaskManager</a>
        <nav class="space-x-4 md:space-x-8 text-lg sticky">
            <a href="#features" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition-colors duration-300">Features</a>
            <a href="#about" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition-colors duration-300">About</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition-colors duration-300">Contact</a>
            <a href="/dashboard" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition-colors duration-300">Dashboard</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="flex flex-col items-center text-center my-12 px-4 md:px-8 animate-fade-in">
        <section class="mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-6 text-glow">
                Level Up with <span class="text-yellow-300">TaskManager</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light max-w-2xl mb-8">
                Organize, track, and accomplish more with TaskManager â€” the free tool designed to simplify your workday.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4 mb-12">
                <a href="/register" class="bg-yellow-300 text-purple-800 text-lg font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full button-bounce transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105">
                    Get Started
                </a>
                <a href="#features" class="border border-yellow-300 text-lg font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full button-bounce transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105">
                    Explore
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="features" class="w-full py-16 bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-70 px-4 md:px-8 glass rounded-t-3xl mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-center text-4xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-10">All-in-One Features</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-gray-800 feature-card glass">
                    <i class="fas fa-tasks text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-600">Effortless Task Management</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg">Organize your tasks, set priorities, and manage deadlines with ease to stay on track.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-gray-800 feature-card glass">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-600">Accurate Time Tracking</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg">Track the time spent on tasks to understand your work patterns and optimize productivity.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-gray-800 feature-card glass">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-600">Real-time Dashboard</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg">Get a comprehensive view of your tasks, projects, and time to make data-driven decisions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="about" class="py-16 w-full px-4 md:px-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-blue-600 text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Why TaskManager?</h2>
            <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg mb-8 text-gray-200">
                TaskManager empowers everyone to keep track of their tasks, manage time, and stay productive with no cost. Start optimizing your workflow today!
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <div class="bg-purple-500 p-6 rounded-lg text-center glass">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-2">Always Free</h3>
                    <p>TaskManager is free for everyone, with no hidden fees or surprises. Focus on achieving more!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-blue-500 p-6 rounded-lg text-center glass">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-2">Secure & Reliable</h3>
                    <p>Your data is safe with us. Enjoy a secure place to store and manage your tasks effectively.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class="py-16 w-full px-4 md:px-8 bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-70 glass rounded-b-3xl text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-8">Get in Touch</h2>
            <form class="max-w-md mx-auto flex flex-col items-center" action="/register">
                <div class="relative w-full mb-4" >
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope absolute left-3 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-400"></i>
                    <input
                        type="email"
                        placeholder="Enter your email"
                        class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-gray-800 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-300"
                    >
                </div>
                <button
                    type="button"
                    class="bg-yellow-300 text-purple-800 text-lg font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg button-bounce transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
                > <a href="/register">
                    Sign Up</a>
                </button>
            </form>
            <p class="text-sm mt-4 text-gray-300">
                By signing up, you agree to our
                <button onclick="showTermsAndConditions()" class="underline ml-1">
                    Terms & Conditions
                </button>
                .
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="py-4 bg-gray-800 text-center text-white mt-12 w-full">
        <p>&copy; 2024 TaskManager. All rights reserved.</p>
        <div class="space-x-4">
            <button onclick="showTermsAndConditions()" class="underline">
                Terms of Service
            </button>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <div id="funFactPopup" class="fixed right-4 bottom-4 bg-white text-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-sm hidden animate-slide-in">
        <button onclick="closeFunFactPopup()" class="absolute top-2 right-2 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">
            <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
        </button>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-2">Did you know?</h2>
        <p id="funFactText" class="text-lg"><%= funfact %></p>
    </div>

    <div id="termsModal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50  items-center justify-center z-50 hidden">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-md w-full">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Terms & Conditions</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
                Please read these terms and conditions carefully before using our service.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
                By using our service, you agree to the following terms:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                <li class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2">
                    You must be at least 13 years old to use our service.
                </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2">
                    We reserve the right to change or update these terms at any time.
                </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2">
                    We are not responsible for any consequences of using our service.
                </li>
            </ul>
            <button
                onclick="closeTermsModal()"
                class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300"
            >
                Close
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>